    "This high threshold ensured that the formulations proposed by the models were not only feasible but also optimized for peak performance.The design knowledge built into the context of the chat models varied in three categories: generic, specific, and none.",
    "The latter simply refers to no design knowledge being provided to the DA and VM.",
    "The aim of this variation was to assess the impact of the richness of contextual information on the chat-based design predictions.",
    "Two reasoning strategies were tested: SFDL and TVDL.",
    "The latter was only used in the case of GPT-3.5-Turbo."
